  "body": "In the spirit of moving away from RPC API for swarm we are putting functionality either to command line or http proxy.\r\n\r\nRecursive download to a directory (traversing a manifest) is provided by RPC `bzz.donwload`\r\nthe implementation of the downloader is https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/master/swarm/api/filesystem.go#L178\r\n\r\nSince access to the local filesystem should not be allowed via HTTP, download to local disk should be supported via the `swarm down` subcommand.\r\n\r\nalso see the effort in #3488",
